IMF’s Blanchard Says It’s ‘Premature’ to Issue Euro Bonds

-- B y   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 
2011-09-20T13:52:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/imf-s-blanchard-says-it-s-premature-to-issue-euro-bonds.html
International Monetary Fund chief
economist  Olivier Blanchard  said today it is “premature” to
issue euro bonds.  “It is probably a good idea for later, it is not a good
idea for now,” Blanchard said at a news conference in
 Washington  following the release of the IMF’s World Economic
Outlook.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kevin Costelloe at 
 kcostelloe@bloomberg.net  